  "title": "7506 - System Application Engineer [ Electrical ]",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>5 Days per week</strong></li><li><strong>SG Office: Jurong East - Tradehub 21 [ Travelling within SG is required ]</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: $3,000 - $5,000 + 14 Days AL + $500 Medical Benefits + Performance Bonus</strong><br /></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><u><strong>Design and improve X-ray scan systems for car park surveillance system or scanning system in Airport or Checkpoint, including building prototypes and testing new designs.</strong></u></li><li>Write manufacturing and test procedures for equipment.</li><li>Install, repair, and maintain equipment in the field while providing customer training as needed.</li><li>Train manufacturing personnel on assembly and testing of products.</li><li>Assist in integrating software with electrical control systems.</li><li>Provide organized documentation for analysis and recommend design improvements.</li><li>Assemble, test, and troubleshoot product designs, offering constructive feedback.</li><li>Evaluate product performance using field data and recommend modifications or improvements.</li><li>Perform other duties as required.<br /></li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree or higher in Electrical Engineering or a related field.</li><li>Min 1-3 years of working experience in electrical field.</li><li>This role is required to visit site [ SG ] if required</li><li>Opportunity to travel globally [ Thailand, UAE ... ] for system evaluations, custom installations, and training purposes.<br /></li></ul><p><u><strong>Must familiar to one of the skills set below</strong></u></p><ul><li>FPGA / DSP / MCU design expertise.</li><li>Experience with interface applications such as Ethernet or PCI.</li><li>Proficiency in programming languages like C++/C# or HDL language.</li><li>Familiarity with electronic testing equipment (e.g., oscilloscopes, digital multi-meters).</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
